Class OutputWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • sci.crayfis.shramp.analysis.OutputWrapper
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    InputWrapper

    public class OutputWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    Encapsulates statistical, image data or mask data and packages it, along with metadata, into a ByteBuffer ready to write to disk. TODO: option for ascii text? ..or should that just go to logger?
